  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK861">
<l>valiyārkku māṟēṟṟa lōmpuka vōmpā </l>
<l>meliyārmēṉ mēka pakai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Avoid offering resistance to the strong (but) never fail to cherish enmity towards the weak.</l>
            </lg>
